&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Technical Product Manager to own Gensyn’s core infrastructure systems -&amp;nbsp; foundational primitives such as &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gensyn.ai/ree&quot;&gt;REE&lt;/a&gt; (verifiable execution of AI/ML workloads) and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gensyn.ai/axl&quot;&gt;AXL&lt;/a&gt; (p2p networking for AI agents) along with the execution, coordination, and training layers that power our decentralized AI protocol.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a 0–1 role. You will shape low-level infrastructure, define developer-facing surfaces, and help identify how our tech reaches real product-market fit.&lt;/p&gt;
