&lt;li&gt;Partner with engineering and research to shape complex systems into usable products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate distributed systems and ML workflows into clear developer-facing abstractions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define APIs, SDKs, and workflows that enable others to build on the protocol.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage directly with technical users (ML Engineers &amp;amp; Researchers) to identify friction and improve usability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and validate early product-market fit through use cases and design partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connect technical capabilities to real-world and commercial outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and track metrics for adoption, reliability, and developer satisfaction.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
